&lt;h3 id=&#34;interaction-between-experts&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#interaction-between-experts&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; INTERACTION BETWEEN EXPERTS&lt;/h3&gt;
