&lt;h2 id=&#34;representing-words-as-discrete-symbols&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#representing-words-as-discrete-symbols&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; Representing words as discrete symbols&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;regard-words-as-discrete-symbols&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#regard-words-as-discrete-symbols&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; regard words as discrete symbols&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;hotel,conference,motel  -  these words respect as a localist representation&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;such symbols for words can be represented by one-hot vectors:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;katex-display&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;katex&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;katex-mathml&#34;&gt;&lt;math xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&#34; display=&#34;block&#34;&gt;&lt;semantics&gt;&lt;mrow&gt;&lt;mtext&gt;motel&lt;/mtext&gt;&lt;mo&gt;=&lt;/mo&gt;&lt;mo stretchy=&#34;false&#34;&gt;[&lt;/mo&gt;&lt;mn&gt;000000000010000&lt;/mn&gt;&lt;mo stretchy=&#34;false&#34;&gt;]&lt;/mo&gt;&lt;mspace linebreak=&#34;newline&#34;&gt;&lt;/mspace&gt;&lt;mtext&gt;hotel&lt;/mtext&gt;&lt;mo&gt;=&lt;/mo&gt;&lt;mo stretchy=&#34;false&#34;&gt;[&lt;/mo&gt;&lt;mn&gt;000000010000000&lt;/mn&gt;&lt;mo stretchy=&#34;false&#34;&gt;]&lt;/mo&gt;&lt;/mrow&gt;&lt;annotation encoding=&#34;application/x-tex&#34;&gt;\text{motel}=[000000000010000]\\\text{hotel}=[000000010000000]
