 &lt;h1 id=&#34;review-main-idea-of-word2vec&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#review-main-idea-of-word2vec&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; Review :Main idea of word2vec&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Start with random word vectors&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Iterate through each word in the whole corpus&lt;/p&gt;
